These are just great trucker/terror/scary/fun movies. I've seen them each, several times, and still get a kick out of them. So, I decided to buy them. When I found this 3-disc set, this was the best way to get them. And, the price is great.

Excellent series of movies.  I like the first one the best because it has more suspense and imagination, more fun and less gore.  The first movie is a great early Paul Walker movie.  The nude scene with Paul Walker is great!  The second and third movies get progressively gorier.  Watching the three together is a slowly building thrill ride.
This is good movies to watch.

I think a big part of the attraction of this series is the "victims" always did something to bring it on them self at the start, and it's usually traffic related. Maybe kind of cathartic for people stuck in traffic when some dunderhead cuts them off, flips the bird and drives on, and you think "one of these days they are going to do that to the wrong person."  These are the films that happens in. :)
